data.description: Sunrise Villas 1 story townhome. Enjoy views of the greenbelt and pool and spa area from your private patio. As you enter this fully updated spacious home.  You enter into an open floorpan living room with vaulted ceilings, fan, and gas fireplace. Built in bookcases complete this updated look along with upgraded flooring. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances. Upgraded kitchen cabinets allow for plenty of storage. All 3 bedrooms have a ceiling fan and light. Community features tennis court and pool and spa.
